{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":952,"text":"Two months ago, my kids and I\nhuddled around a cell phone"},{"time":5160,"text":"watching the live stream\nof the Game Awards,"},{"time":7480,"text":"one of the video game\nindustry's biggest nights."},{"time":10400,"text":"They announced the nominees\nfor the Game for Impact,"},{"time":14080,"text":"an award that's given\nto a thought-provoking video game"},{"time":17160,"text":"with a profound prosocial\nmessage or meaning."},{"time":20960,"text":"They opened the envelope"},{"time":22680,"text":"and they read the title of our video game."},{"time":25920,"text":"An award ..."},{"time":27320,"text":"for impact."},{"time":29160,"text":"It was almost funny, actually,"},{"time":30880,"text":"because I always thought\nthat winning an award like that"},{"time":33560,"text":"would have this huge impact on my life,"},{"time":36240,"text":"but I found that the opposite is true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39840,"text":"The big nights,"},{"time":41280,"text":"the accomplishments --"},{"time":43400,"text":"they fade."},{"time":45000,"text":"But the hardest nights of my life\nhave stuck with me,"},{"time":48440,"text":"impacting who I am"},{"time":50960,"text":"and what I do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53360,"text":"In 2010, my third son, Joel, was diagnosed\nwith a rare and aggressive brain tumor."},{"time":60480,"text":"And before that year was finished,"},{"time":62440,"text":"doctors sat my husband and I down"},{"time":65000,"text":"and let us know\nthat his tumor had returned"},{"time":68280,"text":"despite the most aggressive chemotherapy\nand radiation that they could offer him."},{"time":74080,"text":"On that terrible night,"},{"time":76000,"text":"after learning that Joel\nhad perhaps four months to live,"},{"time":80120,"text":"I cuddled up with\nmy two older sons in bed --"},{"time":83000,"text":"they were five and three at the time --"},{"time":85560,"text":"and I never really knew\nhow much they understood,"},{"time":88680,"text":"so I started telling them a bedtime story."},{"time":92400,"text":"I told them about this\nvery brave knight named Joel"},{"time":96280,"text":"and his adventure fighting\na terrible dragon called cancer."},{"time":101720,"text":"Every night, I told them\nmore of the story,"},{"time":104800,"text":"but I never let the story end."},{"time":106840,"text":"I was just building up a context\nthat they could understand"},{"time":110000,"text":"and hoping that our prayers\nwould be answered"},{"time":112280,"text":"and I would never\nhave to tell them that that knight,"},{"time":114800,"text":"who had fought so bravely,"},{"time":117120,"text":"was done fighting"},{"time":118680,"text":"and could rest now, forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122440,"text":"Fortunately, I never did have to\nfinish that bedtime story."},{"time":126960,"text":"My children outgrew it."},{"time":129160,"text":"Joel responded better than anyone expected\nto palliative treatment,"},{"time":133280,"text":"and so instead of months,"},{"time":134960,"text":"we spent years learning how to love\nour dying child with all of our hearts."},{"time":142080,"text":"Learning to recognize\nthat shameful feeling"},{"time":144640,"text":"of holding back just a little love"},{"time":147560,"text":"to try to spare ourselves\njust a little pain"},{"time":150440,"text":"somewhere further down the road."},{"time":153760,"text":"We pushed past that self-preservation"},{"time":156240,"text":"because Joel was worth loving\neven if that love could crush us."},{"time":162200,"text":"And that lesson of intense\nvulnerability has changed me ..."},{"time":167440,"text":"more than any award ever could."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170400,"text":"We started living like Joel could live,"},{"time":173760,"text":"and we began developing a video game\ncalled \"That Dragon, Cancer.\""},{"time":179920,"text":"It was the story of Joel."},{"time":182760,"text":"It was the story of hope\nin the shadow of death."},{"time":186280,"text":"It was the story of faith"},{"time":188640,"text":"and doubt,"},{"time":190120,"text":"and the realization that a wrestle\nwith doubt is a part of faith --"},{"time":196120,"text":"maybe the biggest part of it."},{"time":198560,"text":"It was a story that began as a miracle"},{"time":202040,"text":"and ended as a memorial."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205840,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207960,"text":"(Giggle)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209240,"text":"(Clapping)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210600,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":214200,"text":"(Video) Dad: Bouncing around,\ndo you like that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217280,"text":"(Giggle)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218520,"text":"I love your giggle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219760,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226320,"text":"(Giggle)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229600,"text":"[A Journey of Hope In the Shadow of Death]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":235280,"text":"[That Dragon, Cancer]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":238320,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":243560,"text":"When you play \"That Dragon, Cancer,\""},{"time":245480,"text":"you're transformed\ninto a witness of Joel's life,"},{"time":249480,"text":"exploring an emotional landscape,"},{"time":251680,"text":"clicking to discover more of what\nwe as a family felt and experienced."},{"time":257240,"text":"It feels a little bit\nlike analyzing interactive poetry"},{"time":261800,"text":"because every game mechanic is a metaphor,"},{"time":264160,"text":"and so the more the player asks themselves"},{"time":266560,"text":"what we as designers\nwere trying to express and why,"},{"time":270520,"text":"the richer the experience becomes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273400,"text":"We took that vulnerability\nthat Joel taught us,"},{"time":276440,"text":"and we encoded the game with it."},{"time":279520,"text":"Players expect their video games\nto offer them branching narrative"},{"time":283120,"text":"so that every decision\nthat they make feels important"},{"time":286680,"text":"and can change the outcome of the game."},{"time":289400,"text":"We subverted that principle\nof game design,"},{"time":292200,"text":"collapsing the choices in on the player"},{"time":295600,"text":"so that they discover for themselves"},{"time":297400,"text":"that there is nothing that they can do\nthat will change the outcome for Joel."},{"time":302280,"text":"And they feel that discovery\nas deeply and desperately as we felt it"},{"time":308080,"text":"on nights when we held Joel\nin our arms praying for hours,"},{"time":312280,"text":"stubbornly holding out hope for a grace\nthat we could not create for ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318960,"text":"We'd all prefer to win,"},{"time":321160,"text":"but when you discover that you can't win,"},{"time":324560,"text":"what do you value instead?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":327600,"text":"I never planned to write video games,"},{"time":329840,"text":"but these moments\nthat really change our lives,"},{"time":332400,"text":"they often come as the result\nof our hardship -- and not our glory."},{"time":337520,"text":"When we thought that Joel could live,"},{"time":339640,"text":"I left the game designing to my husband."},{"time":341800,"text":"I chimed in here and there"},{"time":343880,"text":"with a scene or two and some suggestions."},{"time":346880,"text":"But after the night that Joel died,"},{"time":350480,"text":"the passion,"},{"time":351920,"text":"the possibility of sharing Joel's life\nthrough our video game --"},{"time":356120,"text":"it was something that I couldn't resist."},{"time":358280,"text":"I started writing more,"},{"time":359640,"text":"I sat in on our team's design meetings,"},{"time":362080,"text":"I added more ideas\nand I helped direct scenes."},{"time":365200,"text":"And I discovered that creating\na video game is telling a story,"},{"time":370120,"text":"but with an entirely new vocabulary."},{"time":372880,"text":"All the same elements of imagination\nand symbolism are there,"},{"time":378440,"text":"but they're just partnered\nwith player agency"},{"time":381080,"text":"and system responsiveness."},{"time":384080,"text":"It's challenging work."},{"time":385760,"text":"I have to think\nin a totally new way to do it,"},{"time":388800,"text":"but I love it."},{"time":390480,"text":"And I wouldn't have known\nthat without Joel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394280,"text":"Maybe you're a little surprised"},{"time":396600,"text":"by our choice to share our story\nof terminal cancer through a video game."},{"time":402360,"text":"Perhaps you're even thinking\nlike so many people before you:"},{"time":405720,"text":"cancer is not a game."},{"time":409280,"text":"Well, tell that\nto any pediatric cancer parent"},{"time":411480,"text":"that's ever taken an exam glove\nand blown it up into a balloon,"},{"time":415440,"text":"or transformed a syringe\ninto a rocket ship,"},{"time":418200,"text":"or let their child ride their IV pole\nthrough the hospital halls"},{"time":422360,"text":"like it was a race car."},{"time":424880,"text":"Because when you have children,"},{"time":427000,"text":"everything is a game."},{"time":429640,"text":"And when your young child\nexperiences something traumatic,"},{"time":433600,"text":"you work even harder to make sure\nthat their life feels like a game"},{"time":437680,"text":"because children naturally\nexplore their worlds through play."},{"time":442320,"text":"While cancer can steal\nmany things from a family,"},{"time":445280,"text":"it shouldn't steal play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447880,"text":"If you're listening to me\nand you're trying to imagine this family"},{"time":451480,"text":"that revolves entirely\naround a dying child,"},{"time":455720,"text":"and you can't imagine joy\nas part of that picture,"},{"time":459760,"text":"then we were right\nto share our story with you,"},{"time":462840,"text":"because that season of our life was hard."},{"time":466520,"text":"Unspeakably hard at times,"},{"time":469320,"text":"but it was also pure hope,"},{"time":472000,"text":"deep love"},{"time":473640,"text":"and joy like I have never\nexperienced since."},{"time":477720,"text":"Our video game was our attempt\nto share that world"},{"time":481880,"text":"with people who hadn't\nexperienced it before,"},{"time":484120,"text":"because we never could imagine\nthat world until it became ours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489200,"text":"We made a video game that's hard to play."},{"time":493360,"text":"It will never be a blockbuster."},{"time":495640,"text":"People have to prepare themselves\nto invest emotionally"},{"time":499400,"text":"in a story that they know\nwill break their hearts."},{"time":503880,"text":"But when our hearts break,"},{"time":506240,"text":"they heal a little differently."},{"time":510000,"text":"My broken heart has been healing\nwith a new and a deeper compassion --"},{"time":514919,"text":"a desire to sit with people in their pain,"},{"time":517880,"text":"to hear their stories\nand try to help tell them"},{"time":520919,"text":"so that they know that they're seen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524600,"text":"On the night when \"That Dragon, Cancer\"\nwon the Game for Impact Award,"},{"time":528960,"text":"we cheered,"},{"time":530400,"text":"we smiled and we talked about Joel"},{"time":533600,"text":"and the impact he had on our life --"},{"time":535880,"text":"on all of those hard and hopeful nights\nthat we shared with him"},{"time":540000,"text":"when he changed our hearts"},{"time":541480,"text":"and taught us so much more\nabout life and love and faith and purpose."},{"time":548560,"text":"That award will never mean as much to me\nas even a single photograph of my son,"},{"time":555200,"text":"but it does represent all of the people\nwho his life has impacted,"},{"time":559880,"text":"people I'll never meet."},{"time":562000,"text":"They write me emails sometimes."},{"time":564880,"text":"They tell me that they miss Joel,\neven though they never met him."},{"time":570360,"text":"They describe the tears\nthat they've shed for my son,"},{"time":575920,"text":"and it makes my burden of grief\njust a little bit lighter"},{"time":579760,"text":"knowing that it's shared\nwith a 10-year-old"},{"time":581880,"text":"watching a YouTube playthrough,"},{"time":583920,"text":"or a doctor playing on his airplane\nwith a smartphone,"},{"time":588160,"text":"or a professor introducing Joel\nto her first-year philosophy students."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594800,"text":"We made a video game that's hard to play."},{"time":599280,"text":"But that feels just right to me,"},{"time":602240,"text":"because the hardest moments of our lives"},{"time":604840,"text":"change us more than any goal\nwe could ever accomplish."},{"time":609320,"text":"Tragedy has shifted my heart"},{"time":612000,"text":"more than any dream\nI could ever see come true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616120,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617360,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}